name: Gift Card Box Set
description: Box set contains 6 blank note cards featuring Paul's landscape photography. Includes envelopes.

name: Print of the Month 16x20
description:
Print of the Month July 2010 ﻿– Pumping Station "This photograph is my best selling print. I think it’s because people are proud of the San Joaquin Valley and the beauty found here. The image is made early spring looking west from Hwy. 180 with an orange grove in the middle ground with Mount Campbell and the city of Sanger in the background. To control the contrast of the sky with the low light in the foreground shade I used a split neutral density filter in combination with a sunset warming filter. The Film used was 8” x 10” Fuji Velvia, a very saturated and fine grained film." This limited edition print comes signed and numbered and includes a certificate of authenticity.

Regularly $245
